fields.bio: Dr. Aditi Sharma is a licensed clinical psychologist with over 7 years of experience in treating anxiety, depression, and relationship issues. She uses cognitive-behavioral and mindfulness techniques to help her clients build mental resilience.

fields.bio: Dr. Ananya Mehta is a licensed clinical psychologist with over a decade of experience helping individuals navigate challenges related to anxiety, depression, and past trauma. She believes in a client-centered approach, combining Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT) and mindfulness techniques to empower her clients toward healing and personal growth. Ananya is known for her empathetic nature and her ability to create a safe, non-judgmental space for her clients. She also regularly conducts mental health workshops and writes articles on emotional wellness.
